{"tid":392092,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇女仔請完人食檸檬後會內疚，覺得虧欠左人？","createTime":"2017-09-08T09:21:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-08T14:24:15.000Z","uid":68203,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"04ac0d8796f8ed028a1d15ee703d88cd20434fc0","tid":392092,"uid":68203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T09:21:49.000Z","msg":"上年同一個女仔表白被拒絕，跟住自己都搵藉口話自己好忙所以極少再搵佢<br />\n再一排佢拜拜託我做一件好小極事<br />\n完事後佢去旅行寫postcard不突止仲要寫到成張卡滿晒<br />\n佢今年生日我連happy birthday都冇講過一句，佢就照送生日禮物比我，又寫封萬言書比我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又話好想請我食飯<br />\n比我感覺完全係覺得虧欠左我想償還咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"974c68af556fede4413adfb6dbb75e4d5c35bf1b","tid":392092,"uid":143192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T13:44:40.000Z","msg":"想收你做兵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"639f4adb5b3f722c121395f3766fa20c0bf731f5","tid":392092,"uid":104977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T13:48:39.000Z","msg":"我會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c77e2beb8cf88a0d2bcaab8910ba9f8090b2fb6c","tid":392092,"uid":68203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T14:07:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想收你做兵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n寫信收兵真係夠晒誠意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2ed336316dc32abff1e0faa224d6609ca3f4f35","tid":392092,"uid":130151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T14:24:15.000Z","msg":"會 覺得對唔住佢 同埋想keep住呢個朋友"}]}